    <p><i>(Version 0.7.14)</i></p>
    <br>
    <script>
    /**INSTRUCTIONS -
ENTER YOUR LETTERS IN THE TWO ARRAYS BELOW AND SEE HOW THE CODE NOTICESS PATERNS

